M|Prob|tx|1. **Independence** — Events don't affect each other, but humans don't calculate
M|Prob|tx|2. **Neglect** — Most probability reasoning is qualitative, not quantitative
M|Prob|tx|3. **Correction** — Replace intuition w/ explicit math
